verbose_text: MK-5046 and a modified synthetic bombesin compound [D-Tyr 6, beta-Ala 11, Phe 13, Nle 14] bombesin 6-14 have been shown (in a mouse fibroblast cell line transfected with human BRS-3) to increase p125 FAK, pAKT and MAPK phosphorylation.
